# Roo Configuration

## Package Manager
# Always use Bun for package management instead of npm or yarn
package_manager: bun

## Project Preferences
# This section contains project-specific preferences
project:
  name: based
  type: next.js

## Command Preferences
# This section contains preferred commands for common operations
commands:
  install: bun add
  dev: bun dev
  build: bun run build
  start: bun start
  test: bun test

## Notes
# Add any additional notes or instructions for Roo here
notes: |
  - Always use Bun for package management
  - Use `bun add` instead of `npm install` for adding packages
  - Use `bun dev` to start the development server
